
'''Kumasi Mutiny''' hyɛ ase wɔ Ɛda a ɛtɔ so du nwotwe  March afe 1901 wɔ [[Kumase|Kumasi]]  berƐ a na abanbofuo a wɔn wo Kumasi keka wɔn ho tu ntuo kyerɛ abrofo British abanboguo no.ɛkɔ so saa nna wɔtwe mmiensa esansɛ na temanmufuo abanbofuo no nnya wɔn busumi akatua a abrofo no hyeɛ bɔ no sɛ deɛ British aban no kaaeɛ.

== Abakɔsem ==
Twerɛ a won ka Kumasi Mutiny ka no sɛ Coomassie Mutiny.Abibiman fuo a na ɛshyɛ won a na wɔ de yɛn so no gyinaaho ma abrokyire nkabo.sɛ deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na basabasayɛ nkɔ so wɔ aman biara mo.Dwumakuo a wɔ frɛ wɔn West Africa Regiment wɔ Asantemanmu de wɔn akodeɛ ne nkabomu yɛɛ oyɛkyere maa wɔn adwumakuo adikanfuo hunuuyɛ wɔ afe 1901.

Wei maa abanbofuo a na wɔyɛ temanmufuo no aankɔ anadwo dwabɔ no. ɔyɛkyerɛ no di basabasayɛ baa ma nipa du mmienu hweree wɔn nka wɔ nanwɔtwe mmiensa mu.



wɔ de abanbɔfuo no gyinaa atemuafuo anim wɔ Army Act of 1881, ɛde wɔn kɔ daa ɛfiease wɔ Sierra Leone. Abanbɔfuo no be so ,wɔ bua sɛ wɔn kɔ kum wɔn nanso adwensesa baayɛ.


Private Luseini a na wɔyɛ NCO wɔ British West African Regiment. Luseini ka wɔn a wɔ bua sɛ wonkɔ da ɛfiase wɔ Sierra Leone abraa Kumasi mutiny si yɛ no.{{Reflist}}
